{"url":"https://www.tipton.co.jp/recruit/staff/machine-development/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<title>機械開発の仕事紹介｜人を知る｜株式会社チップトン RECRUITING SITE</title>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"採用,チップトン,新卒,中途,キャリア,求人,就職,転職,開発,設計,機械,メーカー,バレル研磨,海外,愛知\" />\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"常に“明日”に挑戦する開発型企業「株式会社チップトン」の採用情報サイトです。チップトンはバレル業界唯一の総合メーカーです。このサイトでは新卒・中途採用情報をはじめ、社員の声や社内の雰囲気、仕事内容をお届けしています。\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,maximum-scale=5.0,user-scalable=yes\">\n<!--[アイコンここから]-->\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://www.tipton.co.jp/recruit/common/image/sns-icon.jpg\" />\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"../../common/image/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\" />\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"../../common/image/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/vnd.microsoft.icon\" />\n<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"../../common/image/app-icon.png\" />\n<!--[アイコンここまで]-->\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../../common/css/master.css?var=201806\" media=\"screen,all\" id=\"master\" />\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"../../common/css/base/print.css?var=201806\" media=\"print\" id=\"printcss\" />\n<script src=\"../../common/js/jquery.js?var=201806\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../common/js/contents.js?var=201806\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../common/js/pluto.js?var=201806\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../common/js/pluto-config.js?var=201806\"></script>\n<script src=\"../../common/js/slick.min.js?var=201806\"></script>\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n\n#alfooter {\n   position: relative;\n    /*\n    background: url(/recruit/common/image/t180-footer-bg002.png) no-repeat right bottom;\n    */\n}\n    #alfooter .pagetop{\n    position: fixed;\n    right: 10px;\n    bottom:10px;\n    z-index: 90;\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 767px){\n    #alfooter::after {\n        content: '';\n    }\n}\n\n/* alfooter Entry Area\n=============================================================================*/\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area {\n    background: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-footer-bg001.png) no-repeat center top;\n    height: 434px;\n    margin-bottom: 11px;\n    text-align: center;\n    color: #ffffff;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in {\n    width: 1200px;\n    padding: 62px 0;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in .lead {\n    font-size: 18px;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in h3 {\n    font-size: 30px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    position: relative;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in h3::after {\n    display: block;\n    content: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-home-ic006.png);\n    width: 43px;\n    height: 44px;\n    position: absolute;\n    left: calc(50% - 22px);\n    bottom: -57px;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul {\n    margin-top: 120px;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li {\n    display: inline-block;\n    z-index: 50;\n    position: relative;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:first-child {\n    margin-right: 20px;\n}\n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:nth-child(2) {\n        margin-right: 20px;\n    }\n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:nth-child(3) {\n        margin-right: 20px;\n    } \n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:last-child {\n        margin-right: 20px;\n    }\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li.margin-none {\n    margin-right: 0;\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li a {\n    display: block;\n    width: 300px;\n    color :#ffffff;\n    background: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-home-ar001.png) no-repeat #222222 right 11px center;\n    padding: 25px 0;\n    text-decoration: none;\n    box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0 ,0, 0.2);\n}\n#alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li a span {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 767px){\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area {\n        background: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-footer-bg003.png) repeat center top;\n        height: 450px;\n        margin-bottom: 14px;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in {\n        width: 300px;\n        padding: 30px 0;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in .lead {\n        font-size: 14px;\n        margin-bottom: 5px;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in h3 {\n        font-size: 20px;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in h3::after {\n        display: block;\n        content: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-home-ic006.png);\n        width: 43px;\n        height: 44px;\n        position: absolute;\n        left: calc(50% - 22px);\n        bottom: -57px;\n    }\n\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul {\n        margin-top: 85px;\n        width: 100%;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li {\n        display: block;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:first-child {\n        margin-right: 0;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:nth-child(2) {\n        margin-right: 0;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:nth-child(3) {\n        margin-right: 0;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    } \n     #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li:last-child {\n        margin-right: 0;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li a {\n        width: 100%;\n        background: url(/recruit/common/image/t18-home-ar003.png) no-repeat #222222 right 10px center;\n        padding: 17px 0 15px;\n    }\n    #alfooter .alfooter-entry-area-in ul li a span {\n        font-size: 18px;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n}\n</style>\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n<div id=\"body-in\" class=\"staff\">\n\n<p class=\"hide\"><a href=\"#gnavi\">グローバルナビゲーションへ</a></p>\n<p class=\"hide\"><a href=\"#main\">本文へ</a></p>\n<p class=\"hide\"><a href=\"#footer\">フッターへ</a></p>\n<hr>\n\n\n<!--**[Container Header Start]**********************************************************-->\n<header>\n<div class=\"container header-area clearfix\">\n<!--==Header Start=============================-->\n<div id=\"header\" class=\"clearfix\">\n\n    <div class=\"header-area-cover\">\n        <div class=\"header-area-in clearfix\">\n            <!--==Header Main Start=============================-->\n            <div class=\"header-main\">\n                <h1 class=\"logo\"><a href=\"../../\"><img src=\"../../common/image/t18-header-logo001.gif\" alt=\"株式会社チップトン RECRUITING SITE\" /></a></h1>\n            </div><hr>\n            <!--==//Header Main End=============================-->\n            <!--==Header Sub Start=============================-->\n            <div class=\"header-sub clearfix\">\n                <!--==Header Sub Navi Start================-->\n                <ul class=\"header-sub-navi clearfix\">\n                    <li class=\"bt001\"><a href=\"../../\">home</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"bt002\"><a href=\"https://www.tipton.co.jp/recruit/form/entry/\" target=\"_blank\">お問い合わせ</a></li>\n                    <li class=\"bt003\"><a href=\"https://www.tipton.co.jp/recruit/form/entry/\" target=\"_blank\">エントリー</a></li>\n                </ul>\n                <!--==//Header Sub Navi End================-->\n            </div><!--//header-sub-->\n            <!--==//Header Sub End=============================-->\n        </div>\n    </div><!--//header-area-in-->\n    <hr>\n    <!--==SP MENU Start=============================-->\n    <p class=\"menu-btn\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0);\"><img src=\"../../common/image/t18-header-menu001_off.gif\" alt=\"MENU\"></a></p>\n    <div class=\"menu-area\">\n        <div class=\"menu-list\">\n            <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                <li class=\"first\"><a href=\"../../company/\"><span>会社を知る</span></a>\n                    <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/greeting/\"><span>社長メッセージ</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/recruiting/\"><span>求める人財像</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/business/\"><span>ビジネスフィールド</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/culture/\"><span>チップトンの魅力</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/career-plan/\"><span>キャリアプラン</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../company/data/\"><span>チップトンデータ</span></a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"first\"><a href=\"../../technology/\"><span>技術を知る</span></a>\n                    <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/invention/\"><span>開発ヒストリー</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/invention/barrel/\"><span>遠心バレル研磨法</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/invention/mighty-mild/\"><span>重圧バレル研磨機</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/invention/compound/\"><span>研磨用コンパウンド</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/invention/coating/\"><span>コーティング装置</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../technology/patent/\"><span>特許・愛知ブランド</span></a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"first\"><a href=\"../../staff/\"><span>人を知る</span></a>\n                    <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/machine-design/\"><span>機械設計</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/machine-development/\"><span>機械開発</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/development/\"><span>研磨石・セラミックス開発</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/compound/\"><span>コンパウンド開発</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/business/\"><span>国内営業</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../staff/world-business/\"><span>海外営業</span></a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"first\"><a href=\"../../application/\"><span>募集要項</span></a>\n                    <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                        <li><a href=\"../../application/new/\"><span>新卒採用</span></a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"../../application/career/\"><span>中途採用</span></a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </div><!--//menu-->\n    </div>\n    <!--==//SP MENU End=============================-->\n    <!--==Global Area Start=============================-->\n    <div class=\"gnavi-area\">\n        <div id=\"gnavi\">\n            <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                <li class=\"gnavi001\"><a href=\"../../company/\">会社を知る</a></li>\n                <li class=\"gnavi002\"><a href=\"../../technology/\">技術を知る</a></li>\n                <li class=\"gnavi003\"><a class=\"current\" href=\"../../staff/\">人を知る</a></li>\n                <li class=\"gnavi004\"><a href=\"../../application/\">募集要項</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div><!--//gnavi-->\n    </div><!--//gnavi-area-->\n    <!--==//Global Area End=============================-->\n    <!--==lnavi Area Start=============================-->\n    <div class=\"lnavi-area\">\n        <div class=\"lnavi\">\n            <ul class=\"clearfix\">\n                <li class=\"lnavi001\"><a href=\"../../staff/machine-design/\">機械設計</a></li>\n                <li class=\"lnavi002\"><a class=\"current\" href=\"../../staff/machine-development/\">機械開発</a></li>\n                <li class=\"lnavi003\"><a href=\"../../staff/development/\">研磨石・セラミックス開発</a></li>\n                <li class=\"lnavi004\"><a href=\"../../staff/compound/\">コンパウンド開発</a></li>\n                <li class=\"lnavi005\"><a href=\"../../staff/business/\">国内営業</a></li>\n                <li class=\"lnavi006\"><a href=\"../../staff/world-business/\">海外営業</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div><!--//lnavi-->\n    </div><!--//lnavi-area-->\n<!--==//lnavi Area End=============================-->\n\n</div><!--//header-->\n<!--==//Header End=============================-->\n</div><!--//header-area-->\n<hr>\n</header>\n<!--**[//Container Header End]**********************************************************-->\n\n<!--==Container Contents Start=====================================================================-->\n<div class=\"main-container clearfix\">\n<div class=\"wrapper-area underbg clearfix\">\n\n<!--==h1 Start=============================================--> \n<div class=\"h1-area\">\n    <div class=\"h1-area-in\">\n        <h1>機械開発の仕事紹介</h1> \n    </div>                     \n</div><hr><!--//h1-area-->\n<!--==//h1 End===========================================-->\n\n<!--==Wrapper Start=====================================================================-->\n<div id=\"wrapper-under\" class=\"clearfix\">\n\n<!--**[Main Area Start]**********************************************************-->\n<article>\n<div id=\"main\" class=\"clearfix\">\n\n<!--==Main Contents Start=====================================================================-->\n<div class=\"main-contents\">\n\n<!--==Staff Catch Area Start================-->\n<div class=\"staff-catch-area\">\n    <div class=\"staff-catch-area-in clearfix\">\n        <div class=\"left-area\">\n            <div class=\"tl-area\">自分がバージンスノーに<br>踏み込んだような<span class=\"red\">実感！</span></div>\n            <div class=\"name-area\">開発部機械開発課 8年目</div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"right-area\">\n            <div class=\"txt-area\">全開発工程を任された新しい加工機が<br class=\"pc-line\">商品化されたときの喜びは格別です</div>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<!--==//Staff Catch Area End================-->\n\n<div class=\"text-img-box\">\n    <!--==h2 Start================-->\n    <div class=\"h2-area\">\n        <div class=\"h2-area-in\"> \n            <h2>「機械開発」の仕事紹介</h2>    \n        </div>\n    </div><!--//h2-area-->\n    <!--==//h2 End================-->\n    <!--==Text+Image Area Start===========--> \n    <div class=\"text-img-area clearfix clear\"> \n        <div class=\"img-area photo-right clearfix\"> \n            <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"../../common/image/staff/h18-md-ph001.jpg\" alt=\"「機械開発」の仕事紹介\" /></p> \n        </div> \n        <div class=\"tx-area\">主にバレル研磨機の実験機やコーティング装置の新規開発を行います。<br>\n研磨機では設計や3Dプリンターを用いた試作検討等、コーティング機では<br class=\"pc-line\">仕様検討や実際の製造テストを行います。<br>\nたとえばコーティングを行う場合、食材の種類や重量、粒状などによってコーティング槽形状を<br class=\"pc-line\">変える必要があります。そこでシミュレーションを活用し、実際に試作しながら最適な形状を<br class=\"pc-line\">導き出す事で、製品化に結び付けていきます。<br>\nその後、展示会などで自分が開発した機械のプレゼンテーションも行います。</div>\n    </div><!--//txt-img-area-->\n    <!--==//Text+Image Area End===========-->\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-img-box\">\n    <!--==h2 Start================-->\n    <div class=\"h2-area\">\n        <div class=\"h2-area-in\"> \n            <h2>仕事のやりがい</h2>    \n        </div>\n    </div><!--//h2-area-->\n    <!--==//h2 End================-->\n    <!--==Text+Image Area Start===========--> \n    <div class=\"text-img-area clearfix clear\"> \n        <div class=\"img-area photo-left clearfix\"> \n            <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"../../common/image/staff/h18-md-ph002.jpg\" alt=\"仕事のやりがい\" /></p> \n        </div> \n        <div class=\"tx-area\">ゼロからのものづくりですから、常に新しい壁にぶつかります。<br>\nでも当社の発明５訓にある通り、「発明は行き詰まりが出発点」。<br>\n当社は私のやりたいようにやらせてもらえるので、まったく新しい機構を試してみるとか、<br class=\"pc-line\">自由にいろんな挑戦をさせてもらえるのが嬉しいですね。</div>\n    </div><!--//txt-img-area-->\n    <!--==//Text+Image Area End===========-->\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-img-box\">\n    <!--==h2 Start================-->\n    <div class=\"h2-area\">\n        <div class=\"h2-area-in\"> \n            <h2>チップトンで何が育まれたか</h2>    \n        </div>\n    </div><!--//h2-area-->\n    <!--==//h2 End================-->\n    <!--==Text+Image Area Start===========--> \n    <div class=\"text-img-area clearfix clear\"> \n        <div class=\"img-area photo-right clearfix\"> \n            <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"../../common/image/staff/h18-md-ph003.jpg\" alt=\"チップトンで何が育まれたか\" /></p> \n        </div> \n        <div class=\"tx-area\">入社後は新入社員研修で各部門の座学を受講した後、技術課で実務研修、飛島工場で現場実習。<br>\nその後は配属部署にて自社装置の知識、装置設計の基礎を習得しました。<br>\nニッチな業界の為、装置には独自のノウハウがあります。<br>\nこれに新たな開発要素を加えた新製品を生み出すべく、現在の機械開発に携わっています。</div>\n    </div><!--//txt-img-area-->\n    <!--==//Text+Image Area End===========-->\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"text-img-box\">\n    <!--==h2 Start================-->\n    <div class=\"h2-area\">\n        <div class=\"h2-area-in\"> \n            <h2>未来の自分はもっと、輝いている！</h2>    \n        </div>\n    </div><!--//h2-area-->\n    <!--==//h2 End================-->\n    <!--==Text+Image Area Start===========--> \n    <div class=\"text-img-area clearfix clear\"> \n        <div class=\"img-area photo-left clearfix\"> \n            <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"../../common/image/staff/h18-md-ph004.jpg\" alt=\"未来の自分はもっと、輝いている！\" /></p> \n        </div> \n        <div class=\"tx-area\">担当する開発品はお客様先でも新製品の開発に使用されることが多いです。<br>\n試作機がお客様に認められれば、その後は本格な生産機を短納期で求められるため、<br class=\"pc-line\">そのような要求に答えることができる丁寧かつスピーディーな開発能力を磨いていきたいです。</div>\n    </div><!--//txt-img-area-->\n    <!--==//Text+Image Area End===========-->\n</div>\n\n<!--==Staff Message Area Start===========-->\n<div class=\"staff-message-area\">\n    <div class=\"staff-message-area-in\">\n        <div class=\"tl-area\">未来の後輩たちへメッセージ</div>\n        <div class=\"s-tl-area\">大胆に挑戦できるフィールドがここにはある</div>\n        <div class=\"tx-area\">前例がない機械が基本のため、壁にぶつかることばかりです。<br>\nそれを乗り越えるためには、失敗も伴いますが、<br class=\"pc-line\">いざという時サポートしてくれるメンバーがいるため、全力で取り組むことができる環境があります。<br>\nこの経験が自分の財産となり、また、新たな創造に繋がっていきます。</div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<!--==//Staff Message Area End===========-->\n\n<!--==Job Introduction Area Start=================================-->\n<div class=\"job-introduction-area\">\n    <div class=\"job-introduction-area-in\">\n        <h2>別のフィールドで活躍する先輩達</h2>\n        <ul class=\"introduction-slider\">\n            <li><a href=\"../../staff/machine-design/\">